{"id": "c1_c_00018", "url": "https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/yemens-houthis-say-attacked-saudi-arabias-abha-airport-with-drone-2020-10-27/", "time": "2020-10-27", "title": "Yemen's Houthis say attacked Saudi Arabia's Abha airport with drone", "text": "DUBAI, Oct 27 (Reuters) - Yemen's Houthi movement attacked Saudi Arabia's Abha airport on Tuesday with an explosives-laden drone, the group's military spokesman said on Twitter.\nEarlier, the Saudi-led coalition fighting the Iran-aligned group since 2015, said it had intercepted a drone fired by the Houthis towards the kingdom.\nSign up here.\nReporting by Aziz El Yaakoubi; Editing by Catherine Evans\nOur Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles."}
